{"video_id": "XYR_B2uQVU8", "title": "SB 1.19.14-15 | HH Stoka Krishna Swami | 20-05-2023 | Daily Evening Bhagavatam Discourse", "speaker": "HH Stoka Krishna Swami", "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XYR_B2uQVU8", "duration": 954, "segments": [{"start": 0.0, "end": 8.86, "text": " ओम ग्यानति मिरान्धस्य ज्यानां जनिषलाकया चक्षरुन्मीलितं येनातस्मै श्री गुरवे नमः"}, {"start": 8.86, "end": 17.2, "text": " नमाओम विष्णु पादाया कृष्ण प्रेष्ठाय भूतले श्रीमते भक्ति वेदान्त स्वामेन्निति नामिने"}, {"start": 17.2, "end": 30.28, "text": " नमस्ते सारस्वते देवे गवरवाणी प्रचारिने निर्विशेष शुन्यवादी पाश्चत्य देशतारिने जय श्री कृष्ण चैतन्या प्रभूनित्यानन्दा"}, {"start": 30.28, "end": 35.14, "text": " श्री अद्वैत गदाधर श्रीवासादी गोरभक्त वृंदा"}, {"start": 35.14, "end": 39.58, "text": " हरे कृष्णा हरे कृष्णा कृष्ण कृष्णा हरे हरे"}, {"start": 39.58, "end": 43.34, "text": " हरे राम हरे रामा राम रामा हरे हरे"}, {"start": 43.34, "end": 50.02, "text": " ओम नमो भगवते वासु देवाया नारायणम नमस्कृत्या नरम्चेवनरोत्तमं"}, {"start": 50.02, "end": 54.160000000000004, "text": " देवीम् सरस्वतीम् व्यासम् ततो जयम् मुदीरयेत्"}, {"start": 54.160000000000004, "end": 64.52000000000001, "text": " In this session we will be discussing from two verses, the fourteenth and the fifteenth verses of the nineteenth chapter of the first canto of Srimad Bhagavatam."}, {"start": 65.44, "end": 67.4, "text": " So the fourteenth verse is as follows."}, {"start": 67.4, "end": 75.08000000000001, "text": " तस्यैवमे अगस्य परावरेशो व्यासक्त चित्तस्य ग्रहेश्व भीक्षनं"}, {"start": 75.08, "end": 83.44, "text": " निर्वेदमूलो विजशापरूपो यत्रप्रसक्तो भयमाशुधत्ते"}, {"start": 83.44, "end": 86.82, "text": " The meaning of this fourteenth verse is"}, {"start": 86.82, "end": 93.16, "text": " The supreme personality of Godhead, the controller of both the transcendental and mundane worlds,"}, {"start": 93.82, "end": 99.28, "text": " has graciously overtaken me in the form of a Brahmana's curse."}, {"start": 100.24, "end": 103.1, "text": " Due to my being too much attached to family life,"}, {"start": 103.56, "end": 105.06, "text": " the Lord, in order to save me,"}, {"start": 105.08, "end": 108.28, "text": " has appeared before me in such a way"}, {"start": 108.28, "end": 113.12, "text": " that only out of fear I will detach myself from the world."}, {"start": 115.32, "end": 117.17999999999999, "text": " So what is Pariksit telling?"}, {"start": 118.24, "end": 128.07999999999998, "text": " That he considers himself to be an attached householder."}, {"start": 132.96, "end": 135.06, "text": " He is taking a humble position."}, {"start": 135.08, "end": 137.38000000000002, "text": " As a pure devotee."}, {"start": 137.38000000000002, "end": 140.02, "text": " Pure devotees are always very, very humble."}, {"start": 141.12, "end": 144.68, "text": " Even though they are the most advanced transcendentalists,"}, {"start": 145.68, "end": 149.28, "text": " they don't consider themselves as very advanced."}, {"start": 151.42000000000002, "end": 154.48000000000002, "text": " So they are careful not to become proud,"}, {"start": 155.24, "end": 156.58, "text": " not to be arrogant,"}, {"start": 157.36, "end": 158.92000000000002, "text": " not to offend others."}, {"start": 158.92000000000002, "end": 160.92000000000002, "text": " Pariksit is taking."}, {"start": 160.92000000000002, "end": 164.88000000000002, "text": " So Pariksit is taking."}, {"start": 165.08, "end": 168.4, "text": " Especially in front of the saintly persons who have all assembled there."}, {"start": 170.02, "end": 172.04000000000002, "text": " He is taking a very humble position."}, {"start": 172.68, "end": 175.58, "text": " That I am too much attached to family life."}, {"start": 176.4, "end": 179.70000000000002, "text": " I was living in a comfortable palace."}, {"start": 180.4, "end": 185.38000000000002, "text": " I was surrounded by so much of wealth, power, comforts."}, {"start": 186.08, "end": 190.92000000000002, "text": " So in order to make me detached from this world,"}, {"start": 190.92000000000002, "end": 192.92000000000002, "text": " the Supreme Lord has."}, {"start": 195.08, "end": 205.08, "text": " Appeared before me in the form of a brahmana's curse to die within seven days."}, {"start": 207.08, "end": 210.08, "text": " So this is the nature of a devotee."}, {"start": 211.08, "end": 217.08, "text": " A devotee is fully surrendered, a pure devotee especially,"}, {"start": 217.08, "end": 219.08, "text": " is fully surrendered to Krishna."}, {"start": 220.08, "end": 223.08, "text": " And his life is in Krishna's hands."}, {"start": 223.08, "end": 228.08, "text": " So he considers anything that happens,"}, {"start": 228.08, "end": 230.08, "text": " good or bad in his life,"}, {"start": 230.08, "end": 232.08, "text": " materially good or bad,"}, {"start": 232.08, "end": 236.08, "text": " to be the mercy of the Supreme law."}, {"start": 236.08, "end": 238.08, "text": " This is explained in the Bhagavatam,"}, {"start": 238.08, "end": 240.08, "text": " 10th canton, 14th chapter,"}, {"start": 240.08, "end": 243.08, "text": " in the prayers of Lord Brahma to Krishna."}, {"start": 243.08, "end": 250.08, "text": " Tattenu Kampam Susamiksha Mano Bhunjana Evatmakrita Vipakam"}, {"start": 250.08, "end": 252.08, "text": " My dear Lord,"}, {"start": 252.08, "end": 256.08000000000004, "text": " it is only your mercy"}, {"start": 257.08000000000004, "end": 264.08000000000004, "text": " that I am facing some material difficulties"}, {"start": 264.08000000000004, "end": 267.08000000000004, "text": " or some material miseries"}, {"start": 267.08000000000004, "end": 269.08000000000004, "text": " because"}, {"start": 270.08000000000004, "end": 275.08000000000004, "text": " actually I deserve to suffer much, much, much, much more"}, {"start": 275.08000000000004, "end": 277.08000000000004, "text": " due to my own past misdeeds."}, {"start": 278.08000000000004, "end": 281.08000000000004, "text": " But you are so kind to your devotee"}, {"start": 282.08, "end": 286.08, "text": " that you have reduced"}, {"start": 286.08, "end": 289.08, "text": " that suffering that I have to undergo"}, {"start": 289.08, "end": 291.08, "text": " to the minimum"}, {"start": 291.08, "end": 293.08, "text": " as a token"}, {"start": 293.08, "end": 297.08, "text": " to encourage me in my devotional service."}, {"start": 297.08, "end": 299.08, "text": " And that is"}, {"start": 299.08, "end": 304.08, "text": " only because of your causeless mercy upon me."}, {"start": 307.08, "end": 311.08, "text": " So this is the attitude of a devotee"}, {"start": 311.08, "end": 316.08, "text": " when the devotee faces some difficulty"}, {"start": 316.08, "end": 317.08, "text": " or some calamity"}, {"start": 317.08, "end": 318.08, "text": " or some danger"}, {"start": 318.08, "end": 320.08, "text": " or some misery."}, {"start": 320.08, "end": 323.08, "text": " He never blames the Lord,"}, {"start": 323.08, "end": 325.08, "text": " but rather he considers"}, {"start": 325.08, "end": 328.08, "text": " that difficulty to be"}, {"start": 328.08, "end": 330.08, "text": " the Lord's mercy upon him."}, {"start": 330.08, "end": 333.08, "text": " And as a result of that,"}, {"start": 333.08, "end": 336.08, "text": " the devotee becomes detached"}, {"start": 336.08, "end": 339.08, "text": " from everything material,"}, {"start": 339.08, "end": 342.08, "text": " becomes completely detached,"}, {"start": 342.08, "end": 344.08, "text": " 100% detached."}, {"start": 345.08, "end": 347.08, "text": " In the Purport, Srila Prabhupada explains,"}, {"start": 347.08, "end": 351.08, "text": " Maharaj Pariksit, although born in a family of great devotees,"}, {"start": 351.08, "end": 352.08, "text": " the Pandavas,"}, {"start": 352.08, "end": 355.08, "text": " and although securely trained in transcendental attachment"}, {"start": 355.08, "end": 357.08, "text": " for the association of the Lord,"}, {"start": 357.08, "end": 362.08, "text": " still found the allurement of mundane family life so strong"}, {"start": 362.08, "end": 366.08, "text": " that he had to be detached by a plan of the Lord."}, {"start": 366.08, "end": 372.08, "text": " Now, Pariksit is no ordinary king."}, {"start": 372.08, "end": 376.08, "text": " He has appeared in the family of great devotees,"}, {"start": 376.08, "end": 378.08, "text": " pure devotees, the Pandavas."}, {"start": 378.08, "end": 382.08, "text": " And the Pandavas have trained him"}, {"start": 382.08, "end": 385.08, "text": " in spiritual practice"}, {"start": 385.08, "end": 387.08, "text": " because of which he has developed"}, {"start": 387.08, "end": 390.08, "text": " transcendental attachment for Krishna."}, {"start": 390.08, "end": 393.08, "text": " In spite of that,"}, {"start": 393.08, "end": 395.08, "text": " he considers"}, {"start": 396.08, "end": 402.08, "text": " family attachment as very, very strong."}, {"start": 402.08, "end": 404.08, "text": " It is so strong"}, {"start": 404.08, "end": 406.08, "text": " that he had to be detached"}, {"start": 406.08, "end": 409.08, "text": " by a plan of the Lord."}, {"start": 409.08, "end": 411.08, "text": " Now, Prabhupada explains,"}, {"start": 411.08, "end": 414.08, "text": " such direct action is taken by the Lord"}, {"start": 414.08, "end": 418.08, "text": " in the case of a special devotee."}, {"start": 418.08, "end": 420.08, "text": " Lord does not intervene"}, {"start": 420.08, "end": 423.08, "text": " in the lives of everyone."}, {"start": 423.08, "end": 425.08, "text": " Only in the lives of"}, {"start": 425.08, "end": 428.08, "text": " very, very, very great devotees"}, {"start": 428.08, "end": 431.08, "text": " the Lord intervenes."}, {"start": 431.08, "end": 433.08, "text": " Srila Prabhupada explains,"}, {"start": 433.08, "end": 435.08, "text": " in his own life,"}, {"start": 435.08, "end": 438.08, "text": " he was doing business"}, {"start": 438.08, "end": 440.08, "text": " to maintain his family,"}, {"start": 440.08, "end": 442.08, "text": " but he was an ideal grihasta."}, {"start": 442.08, "end": 445.08, "text": " He was very strictly practicing"}, {"start": 445.08, "end": 447.08, "text": " Krishna consciousness"}, {"start": 447.08, "end": 450.08, "text": " and he was following the instructions"}, {"start": 450.08, "end": 451.08, "text": " of his spiritual master,"}, {"start": 451.08, "end": 453.08, "text": " Srila Bhaktisiddhanta Saraswati Thakur."}, {"start": 453.08, "end": 456.08, "text": " But,"}, {"start": 456.08, "end": 460.08, "text": " when Prabhupada faced"}, {"start": 460.08, "end": 462.08, "text": " a lot of difficulties"}, {"start": 462.08, "end": 464.08, "text": " in running his business,"}, {"start": 464.08, "end": 467.08, "text": " he underwent heavy losses."}, {"start": 467.08, "end": 469.08, "text": " So much so that"}, {"start": 469.08, "end": 471.08, "text": " he had to wind up his business,"}, {"start": 471.08, "end": 473.08, "text": " close down his business"}, {"start": 473.08, "end": 476.08, "text": " and leave home"}, {"start": 476.08, "end": 479.08, "text": " and go away to Vrindavan."}, {"start": 479.08, "end": 482.08, "text": " So, he considered that"}, {"start": 482.08, "end": 487.08, "text": " it was Krishna's special blessing upon him"}, {"start": 487.08, "end": 493.08, "text": " that he faced those great losses,"}, {"start": 493.08, "end": 496.08, "text": " that he was forced by Krishna"}, {"start": 496.08, "end": 503.08, "text": " to give up his family,"}, {"start": 503.08, "end": 505.08, "text": " give up the business,"}, {"start": 505.08, "end": 507.08, "text": " engagement,"}, {"start": 507.08, "end": 510.08, "text": " and fully dedicate himself"}, {"start": 510.08, "end": 511.08, "text": " exclusively"}, {"start": 511.08, "end": 514.0799999999999, "text": " for spiritual life."}, {"start": 514.0799999999999, "end": 515.0799999999999, "text": " Similarly,"}, {"start": 515.0799999999999, "end": 517.0799999999999, "text": " Pariksit considers"}, {"start": 517.0799999999999, "end": 520.0799999999999, "text": " that this Brahmana's curse"}, {"start": 520.0799999999999, "end": 522.0799999999999, "text": " is an arrangement of the Supreme Lord."}, {"start": 522.0799999999999, "end": 525.0799999999999, "text": " It's a direct action taken by the Lord"}, {"start": 525.0799999999999, "end": 530.0799999999999, "text": " because of Lord's mercy on Pariksit."}, {"start": 530.0799999999999, "end": 533.0799999999999, "text": " Maharaj Pariksit could understand this"}, {"start": 533.0799999999999, "end": 535.0799999999999, "text": " by the presence"}, {"start": 535.0799999999999, "end": 537.0799999999999, "text": " of the topmost transcendentalists"}, {"start": 537.0799999999999, "end": 540.0799999999999, "text": " in the universe."}, {"start": 540.08, "end": 541.08, "text": " However,"}, {"start": 541.08, "end": 542.08, "text": " assembled sages"}, {"start": 542.08, "end": 544.08, "text": " are no ordinary persons."}, {"start": 544.08, "end": 546.08, "text": " The topmost transcendentalists"}, {"start": 546.08, "end": 547.08, "text": " in the universe,"}, {"start": 547.08, "end": 550.08, "text": " they have come to the earth planet."}, {"start": 553.08, "end": 554.08, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 554.08, "end": 557.08, "text": " the Lord resides with his devotees"}, {"start": 557.08, "end": 558.08, "text": " and therefore,"}, {"start": 558.08, "end": 561.08, "text": " the presence of the great saintly persons"}, {"start": 561.08, "end": 564.08, "text": " indicated the presence of the Lord."}, {"start": 564.08, "end": 565.08, "text": " Why?"}, {"start": 565.08, "end": 567.08, "text": " Why is it like that?"}, {"start": 567.08, "end": 569.08, "text": " Because these great saintly persons"}, {"start": 569.08, "end": 573.08, "text": " carry the Lord within their heart."}, {"start": 573.08, "end": 576.08, "text": " They carry the Lord within their heart."}, {"start": 576.08, "end": 577.08, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 577.08, "end": 579.08, "text": " their presence is"}, {"start": 579.08, "end": 581.08, "text": " the same as"}, {"start": 581.08, "end": 586.08, "text": " the presence of the Supreme Lord himself."}, {"start": 586.08, "end": 587.08, "text": " The king, therefore,"}, {"start": 587.08, "end": 589.08, "text": " welcomed the presence of the great rishis"}, {"start": 589.08, "end": 593.08, "text": " as a mark of favor of the Supreme Lord."}, {"start": 593.08, "end": 596.08, "text": " So, Krishna is favoring Pariksit"}, {"start": 596.08, "end": 598.08, "text": " by arranging"}, {"start": 598.08, "end": 603.08, "text": " the topmost transcendentalists"}, {"start": 603.08, "end": 605.08, "text": " to that holy place"}, {"start": 605.08, "end": 607.08, "text": " so that Pariksit could get"}, {"start": 607.08, "end": 608.08, "text": " their association"}, {"start": 608.08, "end": 610.08, "text": " during the last stage"}, {"start": 610.08, "end": 611.08, "text": " of his life"}, {"start": 611.08, "end": 613.08, "text": " in this material world"}, {"start": 613.08, "end": 615.08, "text": " in order to perfectly prepare himself"}, {"start": 615.08, "end": 617.08, "text": " to go back to Godhead."}, {"start": 617.08, "end": 619.08, "text": " The 15th verse"}, {"start": 619.08, "end": 621.08, "text": " tamopayatam"}, {"start": 621.08, "end": 623.08, "text": " pratiyantu vipra"}, {"start": 623.08, "end": 625.08, "text": " gangachadevi"}, {"start": 625.08, "end": 627.08, "text": " dhrtachittamise"}, {"start": 627.08, "end": 629.08, "text": " dhijopasrishtah"}, {"start": 629.08, "end": 631.08, "text": " kuhakas takshakova"}, {"start": 631.08, "end": 633.08, "text": " dashatu alam"}, {"start": 633.08, "end": 636.08, "text": " gayata vishnugathah"}, {"start": 636.08, "end": 639.08, "text": " The meaning of this 15th verse is"}, {"start": 639.08, "end": 641.08, "text": " O brahmanas,"}, {"start": 641.08, "end": 642.08, "text": " just accept me"}, {"start": 642.08, "end": 645.08, "text": " as a completely surrendered soul"}, {"start": 645.08, "end": 647.08, "text": " and let Mother Ganges,"}, {"start": 647.08, "end": 649.08, "text": " the representative of the Lord,"}, {"start": 649.08, "end": 651.08, "text": " also accept me in that way."}, {"start": 651.08, "end": 652.08, "text": " For,"}, {"start": 652.08, "end": 654.08, "text": " I have already taken"}, {"start": 654.08, "end": 655.08, "text": " the lotus feet of the Lord"}, {"start": 655.08, "end": 656.08, "text": " into my heart."}, {"start": 656.08, "end": 658.08, "text": " Let the snake bird"}, {"start": 658.08, "end": 660.08, "text": " or whatever magical thing"}, {"start": 660.08, "end": 662.08, "text": " the brahmana created"}, {"start": 662.08, "end": 665.08, "text": " bite me at once."}, {"start": 665.08, "end": 667.08, "text": " I only desire"}, {"start": 667.08, "end": 669.08, "text": " that you all continue singing"}, {"start": 669.08, "end": 672.08, "text": " the deeds of Lord Vishnu."}, {"start": 676.08, "end": 679.08, "text": " So this is the right attitude"}, {"start": 679.08, "end": 683.08, "text": " for a perfect devotee"}, {"start": 683.08, "end": 686.08, "text": " who is properly prepared"}, {"start": 686.08, "end": 689.08, "text": " to go back to Godhead."}, {"start": 689.08, "end": 692.08, "text": " That Parikshit is sitting there"}, {"start": 692.08, "end": 693.08, "text": " in the holy place"}, {"start": 693.08, "end": 696.08, "text": " on the bank of the river Ganga"}, {"start": 696.08, "end": 698.08, "text": " in the association of"}, {"start": 698.08, "end": 700.08, "text": " great saintly persons"}, {"start": 700.08, "end": 704.08, "text": " that he is praying to them"}, {"start": 704.08, "end": 710.08, "text": " accept me as a completely surrendered soul."}, {"start": 710.08, "end": 711.08, "text": " Surrender does not mean"}, {"start": 711.08, "end": 714.08, "text": " only surrender to Krishna."}, {"start": 714.08, "end": 716.08, "text": " Surrender means surrender to God."}, {"start": 716.08, "end": 718.08, "text": " Surrender to Krishna."}, {"start": 718.08, "end": 720.08, "text": " Surrender to the spiritual master."}, {"start": 720.08, "end": 723.08, "text": " Surrender to the Vaishnavas."}, {"start": 723.08, "end": 728.08, "text": " Surrender to the saintly persons."}, {"start": 728.08, "end": 730.08, "text": " So this is surrender."}, {"start": 730.08, "end": 733.08, "text": " Perfect surrender."}, {"start": 733.08, "end": 735.08, "text": " And he is also praying"}, {"start": 735.08, "end": 736.08, "text": " let Mother Ganges,"}, {"start": 736.08, "end": 738.08, "text": " the representative of the Lord,"}, {"start": 738.08, "end": 740.08, "text": " also accept me in that way."}, {"start": 740.08, "end": 741.08, "text": " That means he is surrendered"}, {"start": 741.08, "end": 745.08, "text": " even to Mother Ganga."}, {"start": 745.08, "end": 747.08, "text": " Mother Ganga is especially"}, {"start": 747.08, "end": 749.08, "text": " carrying the dust of the lotus feet"}, {"start": 749.08, "end": 751.08, "text": " of the Supreme Lord."}, {"start": 751.08, "end": 753.08, "text": " So she purifies whoever comes"}, {"start": 753.08, "end": 756.08, "text": " in contact with her."}, {"start": 756.08, "end": 758.08, "text": " So Parikshit wants to be"}, {"start": 758.08, "end": 761.08, "text": " completely purified"}, {"start": 761.08, "end": 763.08, "text": " in preparation for going back to Godhead."}, {"start": 763.08, "end": 765.08, "text": " So therefore he is praying"}, {"start": 765.08, "end": 766.08, "text": " to Mother Ganga also."}, {"start": 766.08, "end": 768.08, "text": " Please accept me as a surrendered soul"}, {"start": 768.08, "end": 772.08, "text": " and purify me."}, {"start": 772.08, "end": 773.08, "text": " And also he is telling"}, {"start": 773.08, "end": 775.08, "text": " he has taken the lotus feet"}, {"start": 775.08, "end": 780.08, "text": " of the Lord into his heart."}, {"start": 780.08, "end": 782.08, "text": " He is not afraid of death"}, {"start": 782.08, "end": 785.08, "text": " due to the snake bite"}, {"start": 785.08, "end": 789.08, "text": " which is the Brahmana's curse"}, {"start": 789.08, "end": 793.08, "text": " because he is firmly situated"}, {"start": 793.08, "end": 796.08, "text": " in Krishna consciousness."}, {"start": 796.08, "end": 798.08, "text": " Of course he is requesting"}, {"start": 798.08, "end": 800.08, "text": " the saintly persons"}, {"start": 800.08, "end": 802.08, "text": " to sing the deeds of Lord Vishnu,"}, {"start": 802.08, "end": 804.08, "text": " Vishnugatha."}, {"start": 804.08, "end": 806.08, "text": " So he will be immersed"}, {"start": 806.08, "end": 809.08, "text": " in hearing"}, {"start": 809.08, "end": 812.08, "text": " the glories of the Supreme Lord"}, {"start": 812.08, "end": 814.08, "text": " even at the last moment of"}, {"start": 814.08, "end": 817.08, "text": " his life in this material world."}, {"start": 817.08, "end": 819.08, "text": " The parpocheta Prabhupada says"}, {"start": 819.08, "end": 821.08, "text": " as soon as one is"}, {"start": 821.08, "end": 822.08, "text": " given up completely"}, {"start": 822.08, "end": 823.08, "text": " unto the lotus feet"}, {"start": 823.08, "end": 824.08, "text": " of the Supreme Lord,"}, {"start": 824.08, "end": 827.08, "text": " he is not at all afraid of death."}, {"start": 827.08, "end": 829.08, "text": " The atmosphere created by the presence"}, {"start": 829.08, "end": 830.08, "text": " of great devotees of the Lord"}, {"start": 830.08, "end": 832.08, "text": " on the bank of the Ganges"}, {"start": 832.08, "end": 834.08, "text": " and Maharaj Pariksit's"}, {"start": 834.08, "end": 835.08, "text": " complete acceptance"}, {"start": 835.08, "end": 837.08, "text": " of the Lord's lotus feet"}, {"start": 837.08, "end": 839.08, "text": " was sufficient guarantee"}, {"start": 839.08, "end": 840.08, "text": " to the King"}, {"start": 840.08, "end": 844.08, "text": " for going back to Godhead."}, {"start": 844.08, "end": 846.08, "text": " See when devotees are present"}, {"start": 846.08, "end": 848.08, "text": " they create a completely"}, {"start": 848.08, "end": 850.08, "text": " spiritual atmosphere"}, {"start": 850.08, "end": 852.08, "text": " and in such a spiritual atmosphere"}, {"start": 852.08, "end": 854.08, "text": " one can be perfectly situated"}, {"start": 854.08, "end": 856.08, "text": " in Krishna consciousness"}, {"start": 856.08, "end": 859.08, "text": " an aspiring transcendentalist"}, {"start": 859.08, "end": 861.08, "text": " or even a"}, {"start": 861.08, "end": 863.08, "text": " devotee who is prepared"}, {"start": 863.08, "end": 865.08, "text": " to go back to Godhead"}, {"start": 865.08, "end": 867.08, "text": " cannot get a better"}, {"start": 867.08, "end": 869.08, "text": " atmosphere than this."}, {"start": 869.08, "end": 870.08, "text": " The association of"}, {"start": 870.08, "end": 871.08, "text": " topmost transcendentalists"}, {"start": 871.08, "end": 874.08, "text": " in the universe"}, {"start": 874.08, "end": 876.08, "text": " and"}, {"start": 876.08, "end": 878.08, "text": " Pariksit Maharaj has also"}, {"start": 878.08, "end": 879.08, "text": " accepted the Lord's lotus feet"}, {"start": 879.08, "end": 882.08, "text": " in his heart."}, {"start": 882.08, "end": 885.08, "text": " So these are guaranteed"}, {"start": 885.08, "end": 887.08, "text": " for the King"}, {"start": 887.08, "end": 889.08, "text": " to go back to Godhead."}, {"start": 889.08, "end": 890.08, "text": " And in this way,"}, {"start": 890.08, "end": 892.08, "text": " Srila Prabhupada says,"}, {"start": 892.08, "end": 894.08, "text": " he became absolutely free"}, {"start": 894.08, "end": 897.08, "text": " from all fear of death."}, {"start": 897.08, "end": 900.08, "text": " This freedom from fear of death"}, {"start": 900.08, "end": 903.08, "text": " is a very very important point."}, {"start": 903.08, "end": 905.08, "text": " It is only because"}, {"start": 905.08, "end": 906.08, "text": " of the fear of death"}, {"start": 906.08, "end": 908.08, "text": " and when actually death comes"}, {"start": 908.08, "end": 910.08, "text": " we are so afraid"}, {"start": 910.08, "end": 913.08, "text": " that we are completely bewildered"}, {"start": 913.08, "end": 915.08, "text": " in what we should do"}, {"start": 915.08, "end": 918.08, "text": " when we have to quit the body."}, {"start": 918.08, "end": 920.08, "text": " We try to take steps"}, {"start": 920.08, "end": 923.08, "text": " to take some material shelter"}, {"start": 923.08, "end": 926.08, "text": " or some material"}, {"start": 926.08, "end": 929.08, "text": " remedy"}, {"start": 929.08, "end": 932.08, "text": " or some material attachment."}, {"start": 932.08, "end": 934.08, "text": " All these things bewilder"}, {"start": 934.08, "end": 935.08, "text": " a conditioned soul"}, {"start": 935.08, "end": 937.08, "text": " when quitting the body"}, {"start": 937.08, "end": 938.08, "text": " at the time of death."}, {"start": 938.08, "end": 940.08, "text": " It is a very fearful moment."}, {"start": 940.08, "end": 943.08, "text": " But for a pure devotee"}, {"start": 943.08, "end": 947.08, "text": " it is not at all fearful."}, {"start": 947.08, "end": 949.08, "text": " It is completely free from"}, {"start": 949.08, "end": 951.08, "text": " fear of death."}, {"start": 951.08, "end": 952.08, "text": " I will stop here."}, {"start": 952.08, "end": 953.08, "text": " Thank you very much."}, {"start": 953.08, "end": 954.08, "text": " Hare Krishna."}]}